{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CH8uNhwpuQEHhUGxP5y9Cc","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me create a summary document based on my findings:\n\n## Summary of Findings\n\nI've successfully located and analyzed sample log files and Claude Code agent adapter code. Here's what I found:\n\n### Log Files Located\n\nThe `.cloche/` directory contains many workflow run outputs with several types of log files:\n\n**Sample paths:**\n- `/workspace/.cloche/develop-sharp-vale/output/full.log` - Complete run output\n- `/workspace/.cloche/develop-sharp-vale/output/container.log` - Status messages as JSON\n- `/workspace/.cloche/develop-sharp-vale/output/implement.log` - Agent step output\n- `/workspace/.cloche/develop-sharp-vale/output/llm-implement.log` - Raw Claude Code streaming JSON\n\n### Claude Code Agent Adapter Code\n\nLocated at: `/workspace/internal/adapters/agents/prompt/prompt.go`\n\nThis file contains the complete integration with Claude Code's streaming JSON format:\n\n**Key command configuration (lines 19-23):**\n```go\nvar defaultAgentArgs = map[string][]string{\n\t\"claude\": {\"-p\", \"--output-format\", \"stream-json\", \"--verbose\", \"--dangerously-skip-permissions\"},\n}\n```\n\nThe Claude Code agent is invoked with `--output-format stream-json` flag, which enables streaming JSON output.\n\n### Claude Code Streaming JSON Format\n\nThe adapter extracts text from two types of stream-json events:\n\n**1. Content Block Delta (Streaming Text)**\n- Event type: `content_block_delta`\n- Contains: `{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\", \"delta\":{\"type\":\"text_delta\", \"text\":\"...\"}}`\n- Extraction code (lines 251-265):\n```go\nif bytes.Contains(line, []byte(`\"text_delta\"`)) {\n\tvar event struct {\n\t\tType  string `json:\"type\"`\n\t\tDelta struct {\n\t\t\tType string `json:\"type\"`\n\t\t\tText string `json:\"text\"`\n\t\t} `json:\"delta\"`\n\t}\n\tif json.Unmarshal(line, &event) == nil &&\n\t\tevent.Type == \"content_block_delta\" && event.Delta.Type == \"text_delta\" {\n\t\treturn event.Delta.Text\n\t}\n}\n```\n\n**2. Result Events (Final Output)**\n- Event type: `result`\n- Contains the final message including CLOCHE_RESULT marker\n- Extraction code (lines 267-276):\n```go\nif bytes.Contains(line, []byte(`\"result\"`)) && bytes.Contains(line, []byte(`\"subtype\"`)) {\n\tvar event struct {\n\t\tType   string `json:\"type\"`\n\t\tResult string `json:\"result\"`\n\t}\n\tif json.Unmarshal(line, &event) == nil && event.Type == \"result\" {\n\t\treturn event.Result\n\t}\n}\n```\n\n### Sample Log File Content\n\n**Container.log format** (`/workspace/.cloche/develop-sharp-vale/output/container.log`):\n```json\n{\"type\":\"step_started\",\"step_name\":\"implement\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-05T03:50:18.862643507Z\"}\n{\"type\":\"log\",\"step_name\":\"implement\",\"message\":\"You've hit your limit · resets 7am (UTC)\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-05T03:50:47.49032567Z\"}\n{\"type\":\"step_completed\",\"step_name\":\"implement\",\"result\":\"fail\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-05T03:50:47.491406063Z\"}\n{\"type\":\"run_completed\",\"result\":\"failed\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-05T03:50:47.491446108Z\"}\n```\n\n**LLM log format** (`/workspace/.cloche/develop-sharp-vale/output/llm-implement.log`):\nContains raw Claude Code streaming JSON with message types:\n- `system` - Initialization info (tools, model, session_id, etc.)\n- `assistant` - Claude responses with thinking, tool_use, text content\n- `user` - Tool results\n- `rate_limit_event` - Rate limiting notifications\n- `result` - Final message result with timing and cost\n\n### Related Protocol Files\n\n- `/workspace/internal/protocol/result.go` - Defines `CLOCHE_RESULT:` marker extraction\n- `/workspace/internal/protocol/status.go` - Defines status message types (step_started, step_completed, run_completed, log, error)\n\n### Agent Adapters Available\n\nLocated in `/workspace/internal/adapters/agents/`:\n- **prompt** - Claude Code agent adapter (current)\n- **generic** - Generic command executor adapter"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a50e5552fe0623e45 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 45141\ntool_uses: 35\nduration_ms: 37444</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"65a45440-8ea2-48ce-9346-c9049e4bd586","uuid":"37d6fe50-325d-4574-af5c-93255b717f36","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Find sample full.log or container.log files in the .cloche directory to understand the actual raw JSON content format from Claude Code's streaming output. Look for files matching patterns like:\n- .cloche/*/output/full.log\n- .cloche/*/output/container.log\n- any .log files under .cloche/\n\nAlso look for any Claude Code agent adapter code that might show the JSON format of Claude Code's streaming output. Check:\n- internal/adapters/ for any claude code related adapter\n- Any agent adapter code\n\nRead any sample log files you find to show what the raw content looks like.","agentId":"a50e5552fe0623e45","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me create a summary document based on my findings:\n\n## Summary of Findings\n\nI've successfully located and analyzed sample log files and Claude Code agent adapter code. Here's what I found:\n\n### Log Files Located\n\nThe `.cloche/` directory contains many workflow run outputs with several types of log files:\n\n**Sample paths:**\n- `/workspace/.cloche/develop-sharp-vale/output/full.log` - Complete run output\n- `/workspace/.cloche/develop-sharp-vale/output/container.log` - Status messages as JSON\n- `/workspace/.cloche/develop-sharp-vale/output/implement.log` - Agent step output\n- `/workspace/.cloche/develop-sharp-vale/output/llm-implement.log` - Raw Claude Code streaming JSON\n\n### Claude Code Agent Adapter Code\n\nLocated at: `/workspace/internal/adapters/agents/prompt/prompt.go`\n\nThis file contains the complete integration with Claude Code's streaming JSON format